Package: distiller-genesis
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: distiller-cm5-sdk,
            python3,
            python3-pip,
            git,
            build-essential
Suggests: distiller-examples,
          distiller-docs
Description: Genesis meta-package for Distiller CM5 platform
 This meta-package provides a convenient way to install various components
 for the Distiller CM5 platform. Being a meta-package, it primarily serves
 to pull in recommended dependencies.
 .
 Removing this package will not affect the installed components, which can
 be managed independently. This package is useful for initial setup and
 ensuring a consistent baseline installation.
